I"ù<h3 id="update-the-system-clock"><strong>Update the system clock</strong></h3>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">timedatectl set-ntp <span class="nb">true</span></code></pre></figure>

<h3 id="partition-the-disks"><strong>Partition the disks</strong></h3>
<p class="fs-3">Display partition:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">fdisk <span class="nt">-l</span></code></pre></figure>

<p class="fs-3">Modify partition tables:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">fdisk /dev/the_disk_to_be_partitioned</code></pre></figure>

<h3 id="format-the-partitions"><strong>Format the partitions</strong></h3>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">mkfs.ext4 /dev/root_partition</code></pre></figure>

<p class="fs-3">If swap available:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">mkswap /dev/swap_partition</code></pre></figure>

